These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, firefighter
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, spanish
2 different pets are kept: fish, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, skateboard
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the firefighter is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the owner of the fish is the spanish##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | soy-milk       |
| Hobby         | video-games   | skydiving     |
| Job           | security-guard | firefighter   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | disaster  |
| Nationality   | spanish | thai |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse     |
| Transport     | skateboard    | trike   |

