.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, videographer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, folk
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: horse, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter
1. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | sprite    | mirinda |
| Hobby         | writing        | woodworking  |
| Job           | firefighter | videographer  |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | rock    |
| Nationality   | mexican     | pakistani   |
| Pet           | horse         | turtle    |
| Transport     | airplane           | helicopter      |

